slidingAnalysis.cpp

This tool performs a sliding/adjacent window analysis on coverage, snp and indel along the chromosomes

Syntax:
./slidingAnalysis pileupFolderName outputFolder windowSize windowStep cutOff verbose

pileupFolderName: the path of the pileup folder of the studied organism

outputFolder: the folder where the sliding/adjacent windows will be reported

windowSize: the size of the windows in bp

windowStep: the step of the windows in bp (if windowSize = windowStep an adjacent window analysis will be performed)

cutoff: minimum coverage to call a base

verbose: when it is 1 a verbose output will be generated


